**Differentiation:** Competitors offer colour lists. We offer a decision framework built around interview context, industry, and 2026 aesthetics — so every reader can make the right call for their specific situation without second-guessing.

**Structure plan:** Open with the emotional reality (why nails matter and why you're overthinking it), then move through the decision framework: safe universal choices → by industry → by nail type (gel, press-on, art) → last-minute prep. Close with handoff to new-job-nails.

